      "index": 6,
      "text": "Because I figured out what's behind the recent unusual activity on this planet, it must be the same as other sightings that first appeared in the Capellan March a couple of years ago.\n\nAnd in the process I stepped into witnessing how TMM and the Inheritors have been fighting from control of Mirfak.",
