      "text": "What the Taurians are doing is to systematically clean up competing claims on Mirfak through mercenary contracts through proxy companies like Tauris Majoris Mining to capture and remove illegal or hostile settlements.\n\nEthnic cleansing looks bad on the news, especially when TMM is doing it against the Far Lookers.",
      "branches": [
